374
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:31,480
Not really.

375
00:17:31,480 --> 00:17:32,640
Yes, it is.

376
00:17:33,360 --> 00:17:35,020
Anyway, that's my condition.

377
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:36,640
