421
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:45,560
Hello?

422
00:19:47,080 --> 00:19:47,840
Xiaobai.

423
00:19:48,520 --> 00:19:49,450
Long time no see.

424
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:50,640
