425
00:19:50,920 --> 00:19:53,280
Space Trajectory Design Competition?

426
00:19:55,520 --> 00:19:57,960
It's actually doable.

427
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:58,840
I'll check the problems later.

428
00:19:58,840 --> 00:19:59,800
