489
00:22:15,960 --> 00:22:16,440
Right?

490
00:22:16,560 --> 00:22:19,000
Getting some fresh air is good for you, isn't it?

491
00:22:19,000 --> 00:22:19,400
Here,

492
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,320
