520
00:23:10,960 --> 00:23:13,280
If you want to show off your IQ, just say it.

521
00:23:13,280 --> 00:23:14,400
Stop being so mysterious.

522
00:23:14,400 --> 00:23:15,280
Got it?

523
00:23:20,040 --> 00:23:21,920
The score for the migration scheme competition

524
00:23:21,920 --> 00:23:23,580
