526
00:23:28,160 --> 00:23:31,220
the number and uniformity of the destination planets,

527
00:23:32,200 --> 00:23:34,040
and the fuel coefficient.

528
00:23:36,840 --> 00:23:38,960
Actually, the process of migrating to the galaxy

529
00:23:38,960 --> 00:23:40,960
is about launching ships from the solar system,

530
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:42,920
planting seeds in the galaxy,

531
00:23:43,120 --> 00:23:44,120
and letting them take root and sprout.

532
00:23:44,120 --> 00:23:45,650
The roots grow into trunks,

533
00:23:45,760 --> 00:23:46,960
the trunks grow into branches,

534
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:48,200
the branches grow leaves,

535
00:23:48,200 --> 00:23:50,280
eventually becoming a towering tree.

536
00:23:50,280 --> 00:23:51,520
If you want a high score,

537
00:23:51,520 --> 00:23:53,720
