544
00:24:04,640 --> 00:24:06,480
and low fuel consumption, right?

545
00:24:06,480 --> 00:24:07,410
That's the idea.

546
00:24:07,480 --> 00:24:08,640
You're amazing, Ying!

547
00:24:08,640 --> 00:24:09,800
Come join us!

548
00:24:10,040 --> 00:24:10,800
With Ying here,

549
00:24:10,800 --> 00:24:12,040
