553
00:24:16,720 --> 00:24:18,880
Why would you go out of your way to help outsiders?

554
00:24:18,880 --> 00:24:19,320
Right?

555
00:24:19,520 --> 00:24:20,320
And then?

556
00:24:39,240 --> 00:24:40,400
Is someone coming today?

557
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:41,120
That's a lot of food.

558
00:24:41,120 --> 00:24:42,050
Are you cooking?

559
00:24:42,840 --> 00:24:43,770
You're cooking.

560
00:24:52,240 --> 00:24:52,960
I'll cook.

561
00:24:55,000 --> 00:24:56,480
It's all prepared for you.

562
00:24:56,960 --> 00:24:58,400
