563
00:24:58,400 --> 00:24:59,800
Appropriate. Of course it is.

564
00:24:59,800 --> 00:25:00,440
Please.

565
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:05,080
Here it is.

566
00:25:05,960 --> 00:25:07,090
