575
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:26,130
and you think I'm tricking you?

576
00:25:26,360 --> 00:25:28,280
So do you agree to my conditions?

577
00:25:28,840 --> 00:25:30,300
Forget about conditions.

578
00:25:30,320 --> 00:25:32,040
We Muxing Team are a family.

579
00:25:32,320 --> 00:25:35,120
Don't do that oppression and exploitation stuff.

580
00:25:45,520 --> 00:25:46,720
Why are you looking at me?

581
00:25:46,720 --> 00:25:48,120
He's manipulating me.

582
00:25:48,120 --> 00:25:49,400
Look at him.

583
00:25:51,240 --> 00:25:52,970
There is no manipulation here.

584
00:25:53,160 --> 00:25:54,290
We are all brothers.

585
00:25:54,400 --> 00:25:57,480
Qi did us the honor of eating Wei's ribs.

586
00:25:58,000 --> 00:25:59,800
That means he agreed to join us.

587
00:26:00,200 --> 00:26:01,460
Appreciate the honor.

588
00:26:04,480 --> 00:26:06,480
When did you two sell me out?

589
00:26:06,760 --> 00:26:07,920
We are united.

590
00:26:08,040 --> 00:26:09,400
Do you know what unity is?

591
00:26:09,400 --> 00:26:10,440
We are determined to defeat

592
00:26:10,440 --> 00:26:11,920
the foreign Space Development Alliance team.

593
00:26:11,920 --> 00:26:14,050
This is what you said yourself, Wu Wei.

594
00:26:16,240 --> 00:26:17,440
Alright, agreed.

595
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:22,320
I have one more condition.

596
00:26:22,320 --> 00:26:23,180
Let me tell you.

597
00:26:23,720 --> 00:26:25,380
You shouldn't push your luck.

598
00:26:25,400 --> 00:26:26,360
You shouldn't be insatiable.

599
00:26:26,360 --> 00:26:26,760
At least you shouldn't.

600
00:26:26,760 --> 00:26:28,160
Bring Xiaoba to the dorm.

601
00:26:28,560 --> 00:26:29,200
Xiaoba?

602
00:26:30,280 --> 00:26:31,400
My turtle, Xiaoba.

603
00:26:31,400 --> 00:26:32,800
Can I bring it to the dorm?

604
00:26:32,840 --> 00:26:34,000
As its former owner,

605
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:35,840
it's not too much to ask to see it every day, right?

606
00:26:35,840 --> 00:26:36,520
Not at all.

607
00:26:37,240 --> 00:26:38,000
Really not.

608
00:26:39,360 --> 00:26:40,640
Okay, fine.

609
00:26:41,480 --> 00:26:42,120
Deal.

610
00:26:46,840 --> 00:26:47,680
Words are not enough.

611
00:26:47,680 --> 00:26:49,340
You have to sign an agreement.

612
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:52,960
I have to sign an agreement with you?

613
00:26:52,960 --> 00:26:54,220
In case you can't do it,

614
00:26:54,520 --> 00:26:55,880
there should be some punishment.

615
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:56,520
No problem.

616
00:26:56,520 --> 00:26:57,240
Piece of cake.

617
00:26:57,240 --> 00:26:58,900
Forget about the punishment,

618
00:26:59,000 --> 00:26:59,960
but I can set up

619
00:26:59,960 --> 00:27:01,220
a points system for us.

620
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:02,690
Is that okay?

621
00:27:02,840 --> 00:27:03,400
Okay.

622
00:27:03,920 --> 00:27:04,560
Okay.

623
00:27:06,520 --> 00:27:07,080
Okay.

624
00:27:10,680 --> 00:27:11,640
To be fair,

625
00:27:11,640 --> 00:27:12,680
when Wei's chore points

626
00:27:12,680 --> 00:27:14,000
reach a certain level,

627
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:15,000
Qi has to help out too.

628
00:27:15,000 --> 00:27:16,120
That's not too much to ask, right?

629
00:27:16,120 --> 00:27:16,840
Okay.

630
00:27:16,840 --> 00:27:19,720
When our Muxing Team goes down in aerospace history,

631
00:27:19,720 --> 00:27:21,000
this agreement

632
00:27:21,160 --> 00:27:22,240
will be the token witnessing

633
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:23,640
our glorious beginning.

634
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:31,320
Wait.

635
00:27:33,720 --> 00:27:34,720
This pen won't do.

636
00:27:40,360 --> 00:27:41,880
Once you sign with this pen,

637
00:27:41,880 --> 00:27:43,140
there's no going back.

638
00:27:43,360 --> 00:27:44,620
Is there a difference?

639
00:27:44,680 --> 00:27:46,540
Do you know the origin of this pen?

640
00:27:47,520 --> 00:27:49,400
It has a long history.

641
00:27:49,720 --> 00:27:51,840
Mr. Qian gave it to Mr. Zhao,

642
00:27:51,840 --> 00:27:53,800
and Mr. Zhao gave it to me.

643
00:27:54,040 --> 00:27:55,320
Do you know what this is?

644
00:27:55,320 --> 00:27:56,680
The inheritance of history,

645
00:27:56,680 --> 00:27:57,960
the continuation of spirit.

646
00:27:57,960 --> 00:27:59,480
A globally limited edition,

647
00:27:59,480 --> 00:28:01,240
co-branded by Qian.

648
00:28:03,600 --> 00:28:04,640
Let me see.

649
00:28:08,240 --> 00:28:09,040
Take it easy.

650
00:28:09,600 --> 00:28:11,760
Mr. Zhao is too generous.

651
00:28:11,760 --> 00:28:13,400
Look at who he's giving it to.

652
00:28:34,080 --> 00:28:35,000
Can we start?

653
00:28:38,520 --> 00:28:39,780
Pour me a cup of coffee.

654
00:28:41,120 --> 00:28:42,280
Do you guys want some?

655
00:28:42,280 --> 00:28:43,360
Us?

656
00:28:43,720 --> 00:28:44,600
Do you want some?

657
00:28:44,600 --> 00:28:45,080
They want some.

658
00:28:45,080 --> 00:28:45,960
Three cups.

659
00:28:48,240 --> 00:28:50,440
Don't forget to bring Xiaoba tomorrow.

660
00:28:50,800 --> 00:28:51,520
Okay, okay.

661
00:29:02,760 --> 00:29:04,520
Your brother Xiaoba.

662
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:45,040
Come on.

663
00:29:45,920 --> 00:29:47,280
Time to eat. Let's eat.

664
00:29:47,280 --> 00:29:48,240
Time to eat. Time to eat.

665
00:29:48,240 --> 00:29:48,840
Come on.

666
00:29:49,680 --> 00:29:51,210
Let's serve the rice first.

667
00:29:57,760 --> 00:29:59,490
You are getting better at this.

668
00:30:05,240 --> 00:30:06,520
Let's check the progress

669
00:30:06,520 --> 00:30:07,920
of the data calculation.

670
00:30:08,840 --> 00:30:10,840
You just joined Flight Control.

671
00:30:11,120 --> 00:30:13,780
Keeping up with the pace is a basic requirement.

672
00:30:16,160 --> 00:30:16,880
That's all.

673
00:30:19,000 --> 00:30:19,520
Don't you think

674
00:30:19,520 --> 00:30:22,400
you should have finished it earlier with your ability?

675
00:30:22,400 --> 00:30:24,240
I thought I didn't need to finish it.

676
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:26,000
You have the best qualifications,

677
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:27,720
so you must hold yourself to high standards.

678
00:30:27,720 --> 00:30:29,180
You can't let Mr. Qin down.

679
00:30:29,560 --> 00:30:32,490
You can't slack off, dawdle, or rest on your laurels.

680
00:30:33,440 --> 00:30:34,040
Yours.

681
00:30:34,400 --> 00:30:35,120
The task just started,

682
00:30:35,120 --> 00:30:36,650
so it might be a little slow.

683
00:30:38,200 --> 00:30:39,330
That's acceptable.

684
00:30:44,880 --> 00:30:45,840
Keep up the pace.

685
00:30:48,480 --> 00:30:50,480
You shouldn't be this inefficient.

686
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:52,000
I was worried about making mistakes,

687
00:30:52,000 --> 00:30:53,600
so I checked it a few more times.

688
00:30:53,600 --> 00:30:54,600
Even if you checked it a few more times,

689
00:30:54,600 --> 00:30:56,240
you shouldn't be this slow.

690
00:30:56,680 --> 00:30:57,640
Look at the others,

691
00:30:57,640 --> 00:30:59,040
they are much faster than you.

692
00:30:59,040 --> 00:31:00,360
You have a solid foundation in algorithms.

693
00:31:00,360 --> 00:31:01,760
You need to be bolder.

694
00:31:01,760 --> 00:31:04,000
How can you finish the task at this pace?

695
00:31:04,360 --> 00:31:06,320
Are you going to make everyone wait for you?

696
00:31:06,320 --> 00:31:08,920
I understand. I'll speed up.

697
00:31:11,800 --> 00:31:12,440
You too.

698
00:31:12,520 --> 00:31:13,200
Speed it up.

699
00:31:15,840 --> 00:31:16,960
Well, I think

700
00:31:17,000 --> 00:31:17,800
you young people.

701
00:31:17,800 --> 00:31:18,660
How about this.

702
00:31:19,080 --> 00:31:20,640
After the data is uploaded to the system,

703
00:31:20,640 --> 00:31:21,770
you can get off work.

704
00:31:22,320 --> 00:31:23,440
We'll continue tomorrow.

705
00:31:23,440 --> 00:31:24,120
Go ahead.

706
00:31:40,320 --> 00:31:40,920
Jiajia,

707
00:31:42,240 --> 00:31:43,800
have you heard anything about the professional title evaluation

708
00:31:43,800 --> 00:31:45,680
that was submitted a long time ago?

709
00:31:45,680 --> 00:31:46,560
Any news?

710
00:31:47,360 --> 00:31:49,080
I almost forgot if you hadn't mentioned it.

711
00:31:49,080 --> 00:31:51,200
I remember it was submitted

712
00:31:51,200 --> 00:31:52,280
before the first rendezvous mission.

713
00:31:52,280 --> 00:31:54,080
I've been too busy lately to ask.

714
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:54,800
How about this?

715
00:31:54,800 --> 00:31:56,060
I'll ask Mr. Qin later.

716
00:31:57,320 --> 00:31:59,120
It's not that urgent.

717
00:31:59,560 --> 00:32:02,840
It's mainly because my girlfriend has been rushing me lately.

718
00:32:02,840 --> 00:32:03,600
Girlfriend?

719
00:32:04,320 --> 00:32:05,800
Good things are coming.

720
00:32:06,800 --> 00:32:07,720
Pretty much.

721
00:32:08,280 --> 00:32:09,610
She's coming to Beijing

722
00:32:09,640 --> 00:32:11,500
and looking for a receiving unit.

723
00:32:11,800 --> 00:32:13,640
After coming to Beijing and getting married,

724
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:15,840
we can't still live in the dormitory, right?

725
00:32:15,840 --> 00:32:17,720
So she gave me an ultimatum.

726
00:32:17,720 --> 00:32:19,520
I have to get the title this year.

727
00:32:19,760 --> 00:32:21,290
I need to get a bigger place.

728
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:23,360
Don't worry.

729
00:32:23,360 --> 00:32:25,220
You've submitted so many papers.

730
00:32:25,400 --> 00:32:26,080
As for me,

731
00:32:26,480 --> 00:32:28,760
I've been dragging my feet on this one.

732
00:32:29,840 --> 00:32:31,440
Don't be so anxious, you two.

733
00:32:31,560 --> 00:32:32,760
Especially you, Mr. Li.

734
00:32:32,760 --> 00:32:34,080
Really, Mr. Li, just ask Jiajia.

735
00:32:34,080 --> 00:32:35,960
When I first married my husband right after graduation,

736
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:37,120
we had absolutely nothing.

737
00:32:37,120 --> 00:32:38,400
Our pockets were completely empty.

738
00:32:38,400 --> 00:32:40,130
Life just goes on, step by step.

739
00:32:40,680 --> 00:32:41,200
Really.

740
00:32:41,840 --> 00:32:43,800
If my girlfriend were as calm as you,

741
00:32:43,800 --> 00:32:45,240
I wouldn't be worried.

742
00:32:45,240 --> 00:32:46,640
Her family is well-off.

743
00:32:46,640 --> 00:32:48,240
You know, she can't marry me

744
00:32:48,240 --> 00:32:50,170
and live worse than she did at home.

745
00:32:50,440 --> 00:32:52,970
Look at Brother Hou, didn't he eventually...

746
00:32:54,160 --> 00:32:55,000
It's fine.

747
00:32:55,320 --> 00:32:56,400
Don't overthink it.

748
00:32:56,400 --> 00:32:57,280
I'll ask for you later.

749
00:32:57,280 --> 00:32:58,360
I'll let you know when I do.

750
00:32:58,360 --> 00:32:59,890
You'll definitely be fine.

751
00:33:00,840 --> 00:33:02,080
Okay, thank you then.

752
00:33:02,360 --> 00:33:03,560
I'll be leaving first.

753
00:33:03,560 --> 00:33:04,480
Okay.

754
00:33:05,200 --> 00:33:07,080
Remember to treat Jiajia and me to a meal later.

755
00:33:07,080 --> 00:33:08,080
Sure, no problem.

756
00:33:08,440 --> 00:33:09,160
I'm off. Bye.

757
00:33:09,160 --> 00:33:09,920
Bye.

758
00:33:16,120 --> 00:33:18,560
Mom, when are you coming back?

759
00:33:18,760 --> 00:33:21,120
You promised to tell me a story.

760
00:33:21,120 --> 00:33:22,920
It's been half a month.

761
00:33:23,080 --> 00:33:25,880
Did Chang'e finally meet Hou Yi?

762
00:33:26,680 --> 00:33:28,540
Didn't Dad already tell you this?

763
00:33:28,840 --> 00:33:30,680
Dad's stories are boring.

764
00:33:30,680 --> 00:33:32,600
Dad's cooking is awful too.

765
00:33:32,600 --> 00:33:34,160
I can't even eat it.

766
00:33:34,160 --> 00:33:34,920
Mr. Li,

767
00:33:35,400 --> 00:33:38,160
you've dedicated yourself to the country and your career.

768
00:33:38,160 --> 00:33:39,120
The burden of the family

769
00:33:39,120 --> 00:33:40,520
has fallen solely on me.

770
00:33:41,120 --> 00:33:42,780
Alright, you get back to work.

771
00:33:42,840 --> 00:33:44,370
I'll put the child to sleep.

772
00:33:44,400 --> 00:33:45,600
Say goodnight to Mom.

773
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:46,280
Mom.

774
00:33:46,840 --> 00:33:49,200
Don't work overtime anymore. Come back soon.

775
00:33:49,200 --> 00:33:49,840
OK.

776
00:33:49,840 --> 00:33:50,640
Say bye-bye to Mom.

777
00:33:50,640 --> 00:33:51,320
Bye-bye.

778
00:33:52,360 --> 00:33:53,020
Go to sleep.

779
00:34:00,960 --> 00:34:03,490
The calculation volume is so large right now,

780
00:34:03,640 --> 00:34:05,770
and time is tight for the competition.

781
00:34:06,160 --> 00:34:08,000
I'm really worried I can't do well in both,

782
00:34:08,000 --> 00:34:09,400
and won't be able to stay.

783
00:34:11,600 --> 00:34:13,159
You have your own advantages.

784
00:34:13,159 --> 00:34:14,620
You can be more confident.

785
00:34:17,280 --> 00:34:19,679
The lights in Beijing are so bright.

786
00:34:20,800 --> 00:34:22,000
So bright that I can only see

787
00:34:22,000 --> 00:34:24,120
the brightest stars in the sky.

788
00:34:25,840 --> 00:34:26,719
You know what?

789
00:34:27,360 --> 00:34:28,600
In my hometown,

790
00:34:29,440 --> 00:34:30,969
as soon as the sun goes down,

791
00:34:31,320 --> 00:34:33,179
everyone basically goes to rest.

792
00:34:33,560 --> 00:34:34,440
With no lights,

793
00:34:34,880 --> 00:34:37,280
all the stars in the sky can be seen.

794
00:34:38,400 --> 00:34:39,600
When I was young,

795
00:34:40,320 --> 00:34:42,560
to get into my dream school

796
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:44,360
and to come to Beijing,

797
00:34:44,719 --> 00:34:47,199
I worked desperately hard on practice questions

798
00:34:47,199 --> 00:34:48,460
and memorizing texts.

799
00:34:50,719 --> 00:34:52,520
When everyone else was resting,

800
00:34:53,120 --> 00:34:54,850
only the stars accompanied me.

801
00:34:57,000 --> 00:34:59,260
I chose to come to Flight Control at first

802
00:34:59,360 --> 00:35:00,760
to play it safe.

803
00:35:02,600 --> 00:35:06,160
I wanted to stay in this city that's brighter than the stars.

804
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:09,860
But I didn't expect

805
00:35:10,440 --> 00:35:12,400
that after coming here, I'd find

806
00:35:13,040 --> 00:35:15,880
this place is full of hidden talents.

807
00:35:17,120 --> 00:35:19,840
The sense of inferiority I had when I first entered college

808
00:35:19,840 --> 00:35:20,880
came back.

809
00:35:23,280 --> 00:35:24,880
Actually, I quite envy you.

810
00:35:25,960 --> 00:35:28,800
You are not only capable and strong,

811
00:35:29,320 --> 00:35:32,050
but your ideas for proposals are also very clear.

812
00:35:32,320 --> 00:35:33,120
Unlike me,

813
00:35:34,240 --> 00:35:36,880
I couldn't help with the flight simulation task.

814
00:35:36,880 --> 00:35:38,800
And now, with the relay satellite data,

815
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:40,680
I'm working slower than all of you.

816
00:35:40,680 --> 00:35:41,680
Don't be discouraged.

817
00:35:41,680 --> 00:35:43,940
Work is different from school after all.

818
00:35:44,840 --> 00:35:46,360
Oh, and there's Wu Wei.

819
00:35:47,320 --> 00:35:49,600
Actually, after interacting with him these days,

820
00:35:49,600 --> 00:35:51,400
I found he's quite unique.

821
00:35:52,000 --> 00:35:53,360
He has this

822
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:55,320
reckless courage.

823
00:35:55,920 --> 00:35:57,000
I just feel

824
00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:58,930
he can succeed at whatever he does.

825
00:35:59,280 --> 00:36:01,480
If he has a dream, he'll pursue it.

826
00:36:02,200 --> 00:36:03,080
I believe

827
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:05,240
even if the simulation failed this time,

828
00:36:05,240 --> 00:36:06,440
and he took a hit,

829
00:36:06,720 --> 00:36:08,880
he'll get right back up and keep going.

830
00:36:09,560 --> 00:36:11,240
Ying Ziqi, you know what?

831
00:36:12,200 --> 00:36:14,480
You two are actually quite similar.

832
00:36:15,760 --> 00:36:16,560
Him and me?

833
00:36:17,400 --> 00:36:18,040
Similar?

834
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:20,640
Even though I'm a STEM girl,

835
00:36:20,640 --> 00:36:22,920
I'm actually a very good judge of character.

836
00:36:22,920 --> 00:36:24,850
You both have a kind of confidence.

837
00:36:25,400 --> 00:36:27,440
Yours comes from your competence,

838
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:30,240
and Wu Wei's comes from his persistence.

839
00:36:31,480 --> 00:36:32,810
I have neither of these.

840
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:35,320
I came to Beijing,

841
00:36:35,760 --> 00:36:37,440
and I can only rely on myself.

842
00:36:39,040 --> 00:36:39,720
Here,

843
00:36:40,360 --> 00:36:42,160
I face even greater challenges.

844
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:45,240
You are right.

845
00:36:45,880 --> 00:36:48,680
This is a place where you stay based on competence.

846
00:36:48,880 --> 00:36:50,120
If I want to stay,

847
00:36:51,040 --> 00:36:53,080
I have to rely on my own competence

848
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:55,140
and move forward step by step.

849
00:37:00,720 --> 00:37:02,580
Actually, I really envy you guys.

850
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:06,640
Envy us?

851
00:37:07,480 --> 00:37:08,940
I envy that you have dreams

852
00:37:09,600 --> 00:37:10,860
and can fight for them.

853
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:13,770
I even envy you for having pressure

854
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:15,140
that can motivate you.

855
00:37:15,600 --> 00:37:16,600
As for me,

856
00:37:17,240 --> 00:37:19,900
I'm like a satellite that hasn't entered orbit.

857
00:37:20,440 --> 00:37:25,280
We strive for a stable job

858
00:37:26,200 --> 00:37:27,840
and a residency status.

859
00:37:28,880 --> 00:37:29,880
For such simple,

860
00:37:30,520 --> 00:37:32,640
even somewhat

861
00:37:32,640 --> 00:37:34,000
vulgar dreams,

862
00:37:34,840 --> 00:37:36,040
you actually envy us?

863
00:37:36,320 --> 00:37:37,960
How can dreams be ranked?

864
00:37:42,640 --> 00:37:44,160
This is my

865
00:37:44,560 --> 00:37:46,620
first time hearing someone say that.

866
00:37:46,960 --> 00:37:48,820
A very annoying person once said,

867
00:37:49,040 --> 00:37:50,280
passion itself

868
00:37:51,200 --> 00:37:52,660
is the meaning of passion.

869
00:37:53,560 --> 00:37:54,200
Who?

870
00:37:56,040 --> 00:37:58,440
Eat. It relieves stress.

871
00:38:00,880 --> 00:38:01,480
Thank you.

872
00:38:03,680 --> 00:38:06,120
The plan for the track competition is so hard.

873
00:38:06,120 --> 00:38:09,000
Jia's assignment isn't done either. What should we do?

874
00:38:09,000 --> 00:38:11,660
The track data in our plan is the difficult part.

875
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:14,330
I think Jia has done a similar plan before.

876
00:38:14,520 --> 00:38:15,520
That's great.

877
00:38:17,280 --> 00:38:18,000
Wei.

878
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:19,760
Jia is your boss.

879
00:38:20,440 --> 00:38:22,000
Go ask her for it so we can use it as a reference.

880
00:38:22,000 --> 00:38:24,280
I think it could work.

881
00:38:24,920 --> 00:38:26,480
But how do I bring it up?

882
00:38:27,120 --> 00:38:30,250
I entered the competition behind her back to begin with.

883
00:38:31,320 --> 00:38:32,320
You know how it is.

884
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:32,960
Wei.

885
00:38:33,680 --> 00:38:35,000
I'll teach you a trick.

886
00:38:35,000 --> 00:38:36,440
Just flatter her like crazy.

887
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:38,360
Flatter her hard, nonstop.

888
00:38:38,720 --> 00:38:40,400
Trust me, in less than three days,

889
00:38:40,400 --> 00:38:41,660
no one can resist that.

890
00:38:42,640 --> 00:38:43,200
Really?

891
00:38:43,200 --> 00:38:44,080
Come on.

892
00:38:44,680 --> 00:38:45,280
Come on.

893
00:38:46,280 --> 00:38:48,080
Nothing ventured, nothing gained.

894
00:38:48,080 --> 00:38:49,280
If we can get the data,

895
00:38:49,280 --> 00:38:50,760
it'll save us a lot of time.

896
00:38:50,880 --> 00:38:51,640
You know

897
00:38:51,640 --> 00:38:53,640
how tight our schedule is right now.

898
00:38:53,640 --> 00:38:55,240
Yeah, I know, but

899
00:38:56,640 --> 00:38:57,480
how do I flatter her?

900
00:38:57,480 --> 00:38:59,080
I, Cai, will teach you.

901
00:38:59,200 --> 00:39:01,530
Workplace flattery has three main steps.

902
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:02,800
Step one,

903
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:04,400
start with her work ability.

904
00:39:04,400 --> 00:39:06,800
Ask for advice humbly to make her look good.

905
00:39:07,480 --> 00:39:09,360
Step two, start with the details.

906
00:39:09,720 --> 00:39:11,320
Show concern for her well-being.

907
00:39:11,320 --> 00:39:12,880
Step three is the most important.

908
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:14,610
Be persistent and relentless.

909
00:39:18,320 --> 00:39:19,380
Give me an example.

910
00:39:19,400 --> 00:39:20,480
Give us an example.

911
00:39:22,520 --> 00:39:24,520
Qi loves chocolate, right?

912
00:39:24,880 --> 00:39:26,340
Do you know how to flatter?

913
00:39:28,240 --> 00:39:29,000
Ying Ziqi.

914
00:39:29,360 --> 00:39:30,820
You are like my chocolate,

915
00:39:32,240 --> 00:39:33,440
sweet, cute,

916
00:39:34,200 --> 00:39:35,040
and beautiful.

917
00:39:35,040 --> 00:39:36,100
Alright, alright.

918
00:39:48,480 --> 00:39:49,000
Chinese ship.

919
00:39:49,000 --> 00:39:51,240
Why do people flatter?

920
00:39:51,240 --> 00:39:52,760
I skipped breakfast and feel a bit hungry.

921
00:39:52,760 --> 00:39:53,680
Does anyone have food?

922
00:39:53,680 --> 00:39:55,080
I have some bread in my drawer.

923
00:39:55,080 --> 00:39:56,480
I'll give it to you later.

924
00:39:56,560 --> 00:39:57,640
I didn't sleep well last night.

925
00:39:57,640 --> 00:39:58,840
I'm a little sleepy now.

926
00:39:58,840 --> 00:40:00,000
I'll go get some water.

927
00:40:00,000 --> 00:40:01,000
Wu Wei.

928
00:40:02,200 --> 00:40:02,760
Jia, Yan,

929
00:40:02,760 --> 00:40:03,760
Li, Xiu, morning.

930
00:40:04,360 --> 00:40:06,680
Why are you suddenly so enthusiastic?

931
00:40:08,240 --> 00:40:09,960
He's finally figured it out

932
00:40:09,960 --> 00:40:11,360
and learned to respect his seniors.

933
00:40:11,360 --> 00:40:13,600
A good day starts in the morning.

934
00:40:14,040 --> 00:40:16,100
Why are you suddenly so hardworking?

935
00:40:16,480 --> 00:40:17,960
The floor is so dirty, but you don't sweep it.

936
00:40:17,960 --> 00:40:19,680
Why are you cleaning the ceiling?

937
00:40:19,680 --> 00:40:20,760
Because my seniors

938
00:40:20,760 --> 00:40:21,680
are my ceiling.

939
00:40:22,560 --> 00:40:23,880
That's a good one.

940
00:40:23,880 --> 00:40:24,840
Keep it up.

941
00:40:24,840 --> 00:40:27,500
Don't forget it once your enthusiasm wears off.

942
00:40:28,160 --> 00:40:29,080
Then later,

943
00:40:29,080 --> 00:40:29,240
while you're at it,

944
00:40:29,240 --> 00:40:30,560
take out the trash, will you?

945
00:40:30,560 --> 00:40:31,320
No problem.

946
00:40:37,600 --> 00:40:38,400
Oh my god, Jia.

947
00:40:39,960 --> 00:40:40,560
Jia.

948
00:40:40,800 --> 00:40:42,200
Look at the way you walk.

949
00:40:42,200 --> 00:40:44,530
People would think you're a runway model.

950
00:40:45,680 --> 00:40:45,960
Jia,

951
00:40:45,960 --> 00:40:47,720
you are indeed the beauty of our flight control center.

952
00:40:47,720 --> 00:40:50,320
With your figure, it's a waste not to be a model.

953
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:55,260
How does the saying go?

954
00:40:56,160 --> 00:40:57,680
You're a runaway princess.

955
00:40:57,680 --> 00:40:59,480
Did you take the wrong medicine?

956
00:41:00,640 --> 00:41:01,240
Jia,

957
00:41:01,240 --> 00:41:03,120
you are so dazzling, so brilliant,

958
00:41:03,120 --> 00:41:03,960
and radiant.

959
00:41:03,960 --> 00:41:06,090
You warm and shine upon us like the sun.

960
00:41:07,840 --> 00:41:09,280
Don't you like hearing that, Jia?

961
00:41:09,280 --> 00:41:10,080
Are you drunk?

962
00:41:10,320 --> 00:41:11,520
Or still half asleep?

963
00:41:12,160 --> 00:41:13,890
Or just have too much free time?

964
00:41:14,120 --> 00:41:16,240
No, I just can't help myself around you, Jia.

965
00:41:16,240 --> 00:41:17,480
It's uncontrollable. My heart is fluttering.

966
00:41:17,480 --> 00:41:18,280
Okay, enough.

967
00:41:18,840 --> 00:41:22,160
If you're sick, see a doctor. If you're unwell, take a leave.

968
00:41:22,160 --> 00:41:24,920
I'm just full of admiration for you, Jia,

969
00:41:24,920 --> 00:41:26,380
and want to learn from you.

970
00:41:29,880 --> 00:41:30,760
All right.

971
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:33,850
Finish cleaning and get back to work quickly.

972
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:34,760
Yes.

973
00:41:35,240 --> 00:41:36,040
Wait a minute.

974
00:41:37,040 --> 00:41:39,100
Didn't you want to learn and improve?

975
00:41:39,800 --> 00:41:40,730
That's perfect.

976
00:41:40,840 --> 00:41:42,800
Before you get to work,

977
00:41:43,520 --> 00:41:45,360
the ceiling on

978
00:41:45,680 --> 00:41:48,280
this entire floor isn't very clean.

979
00:41:48,560 --> 00:41:49,480
It needs to be cleaned.

980
00:41:49,480 --> 00:41:50,280
We aerospace professionals

981
00:41:50,280 --> 00:41:52,640
must be well-rounded in all aspects.

982
00:41:52,960 --> 00:41:54,400
The entire floor?

983
00:41:54,520 --> 00:41:55,760
What, you don't want to?

984
00:41:55,760 --> 00:41:56,600
Okay.

985
00:41:56,680 --> 00:41:57,610
Then get to work.

986
00:42:00,560 --> 00:42:02,240
The entire floor.

987
00:42:07,200 --> 00:42:09,260
You just want to tire the poor guy out.

988
00:42:16,320 --> 00:42:17,320
How did it go, Wei?

989
00:42:17,720 --> 00:42:18,640
What do you mean?

990
00:42:18,640 --> 00:42:19,680
She didn't buy it at all,

991
00:42:19,680 --> 00:42:21,080
and even said I was crazy.

992
00:42:22,760 --> 00:42:24,120
Is it your problem

993
00:42:24,120 --> 00:42:25,720
or mine?

994
00:42:27,400 --> 00:42:29,200
How could it be my problem?

995
00:42:29,440 --> 00:42:31,170
Besides, why would I set you up?

996
00:42:31,760 --> 00:42:33,490
I suggest you guys just give up.

997
00:42:33,680 --> 00:42:34,920
Don't underestimate Jia.

998
00:42:34,920 --> 00:42:37,180
Your trick definitely won't work on her.

999
00:42:37,760 --> 00:42:39,690
My trick is absolutely foolproof.

1000
00:42:39,960 --> 00:42:41,200
Do you know what

1001
00:42:41,200 --> 00:42:42,440
the key to my trick is?

1002
00:42:43,440 --> 00:42:44,440
Be thick-skinned

1003
00:42:44,440 --> 00:42:45,520
and persistent.

1004
00:42:49,640 --> 00:42:50,480
Persistent.

1005
